description: The investment objective of the FT Vest U.S. Equity Buffer ETF - October (the "Fund") is to seek to provide investors with returns (before fees and expenses) that match the price return of the SPDR S&P 500 ETF Trust (the "Underlying ETF"), up to a predetermined upside cap of 14.09% while providing a buffer (before fees and expenses) against the first 10% of Underlying ETF losses, over the period from October 21, 2024 to October 17, 2025.
name: FT Vest U.S. Equity Buffer ETF - October
